The official currency of the [[Organisation of Free Cities (OFC)|OFC]]. It manifests as a glowing purple tattoo on a persons body, typically on the upper arm. The Credit system is not transferable to Gold or other currencies. You must have access to a spell to be able to transfer currency for purchases. [[Chenris Tallfellow â€¡]] is the only member of [[the party]] with access to this spell. The Credit system also allows people to go into debt and even give loans to people. The tattoo is only visible when you're in [[Organisation of Free Cities (OFC)|OFC]] territory. 